    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/Compass.tsx` component. It renders an elegant, interactive compass dial with dual themes: a soft pink pastel \"Milk Tea\" boba theme and a futuristic cyberpunk \"Drinker\" violet neon glow theme. It includes a dial rotation slider so desktop users can simulate changing their heading, a locking arrow that points directly to the nearest/selected shop, and live coordinates and heading stats."
